===Ned===
* '''Player:''' Trick or treat!
* {{tcond|If the player hasn't received treats from Ned:}}
** '''Ned:''' Aye, what a good costume!
** '''Ned:''' That would scare any old sailor, and I've seen my fair share of things!
** '''Player:''' Do you get much business around Halloween?
** '''Ned:''' Actually, not too bad! For the most part they need some ropes for tying hay bales.
** '''Ned:''' But the bulk of my business at the moment is sailing rigs.
** '''Player:''' Do they require particular maintenance at this time of year?
** '''Ned:''' No, but I have heard that they are considering allowing less experienced sailors to sail the seas!
** '''Ned:''' I think it'll just mean an increase of shipwrecks, if you ask me! But it is good for my business.
** '''Player:''' Oh, that does sound interesting! I wonder if they'll let me?
** '''Ned:''' Maybe in a year or so? Meanwhile, I'd better get to work right away.
** '''Player:''' I'll leave you to it then.
** '''Player:''' Is there anyone else who'd like to see my costume?
** {{tact|continues}}
* {{tcond|If the player has already received treats from Ned:}}
** '''Ned:''' Oh hello again!
** '''Ned:''' Here for some rope or to show me the results of your sweet plundering?
** '''Player:''' I have not been plundering, I have been Trick-or- Treating properly!
** '''Player:''' People have been kind to me, for the most part! I might have been victim of the odd trick myself.
** '''Ned:''' That sounds like quite a tale! Maybe for some other time!
** '''Player:''' Maybe! In the meantime, do you know who else would like to see my costume?
** {{tact|continues}}
* {{tcond|If the player has trick-or-treated everyone:}}
** '''Ned:''' I believe you've visited the most generous of us!
** '''Ned:''' The citizens are still as eager as ever, though, and I hear Varrock is the place to be for Trick-or-Treaters!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{trandom}}
